These are proposed milestones for the DHC WG recharter:

Jul 2013  Send failover requirements to IESG for publication
Jul 2013  Send option guidelines to IESG for publication
Jul 2013  Send SOLMAXRT to IESG for publication
Oct 2013  Send issues with stateful options to IESG for publication
Oct 2013  Send failover design to IESG for publication
Nov 2013  Assign editor and core team for 3315-bis work
Nov 2014  Do WGLC on 3315-bis
Apr 2015  Send 3315-bis to IESG
